  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/daac9f5969ee0309fcd9d2509d4887d3.avif?t=1757339011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras_big/daac9f5969ee0309fcd9d2509d4887d3.avif?t=1757339011 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PathUp!</strong> is an adventure-packed game where you face a challenging climb. Overcome obstacles, combine different mechanics, and prove that you can conquer the summit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you reach your goal?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>PathUp!</strong>, you embark on an unforgettable journey to climb to the top. Along the way, you’ll face narrow paths, steep inclines, and sharp turns that demand quick decisions and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you’ll need to master a set of unique mechanics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>Boost</strong> – Speed bursts to overcome difficult sections.<br>🦘 <strong>Jump / Double Jump</strong> – Use powerful jumps to clear obstacles. Time your second jump during the brief glowing pulse to succeed!<br>⬅️➡️ <strong>Impulse Left / Impulse Right</strong> – Make precise adjustments mid-air or on the ground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful — one mistake can send you tumbling back! The path is tough, and every second counts. Your skill, reflexes, and timing will determine how far you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 Don’t worry — the game includes multiple <strong>checkpoints</strong>, so if you fall, you can try again from a safe spot without starting over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗💨 <strong>Check out the GIFs below</strong> to see these mechanics in action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Checkpoint</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/4c2b873855a3ee908d020e726af5dccd.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/4c2b873855a3ee908d020e726af5dccd.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/4c2b873855a3ee908d020e726af5dccd.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>✔️ <strong>Jump</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/60d9b085fb06f48526d9df760b282b0a.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/60d9b085fb06f48526d9df760b282b0a.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/60d9b085fb06f48526d9df760b282b0a.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Jump + Impulse Left</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/aadc23724e0e2c2f57160075ac927bb7.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/aadc23724e0e2c2f57160075ac927bb7.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/aadc23724e0e2c2f57160075ac927bb7.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>✔️ <strong>Jump + Impulse Right</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/b768b533962125882410378fde1fe6b1.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/b768b533962125882410378fde1fe6b1.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/b768b533962125882410378fde1fe6b1.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>✔️ <strong>Turbo + Jump</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/04ca584eb67fb211e208b786118e5387.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/04ca584eb67fb211e208b786118e5387.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/04ca584eb67fb211e208b786118e5387.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>✔️ Duble<strong>Jump</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/e26ef5da1b6775561594f534ac79b5f0.poster.avif?t=1757339011\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/e26ef5da1b6775561594f534ac79b5f0.webm?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/e26ef5da1b6775561594f534ac79b5f0.mp4?t=1757339011\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your adventure now, overcome every challenge, and reach the summit! ⛰️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras/daac9f5969ee0309fcd9d2509d4887d3.avif?t=1757339011\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466310/extras_big/daac9f5969ee0309fcd9d2509d4887d3.avif?t=1757339011 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PathUp!</strong> is an adventure-packed game where you face a challenging climb. Overcome obstacles, combine different mechanics, and prove that you can conquer the summit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you reach your goal?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>PathUp!</strong>, you embark on an unforgettable journey to climb to the top. Along the way, you’ll face narrow paths, steep inclines, and sharp turns that demand quick decisions and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you’ll need to master a set of unique mechanics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>Boost</strong> – Speed bursts to overcome difficult sections.<br>🦘 <strong>Jump / Double Jump</strong> – Use powerful jumps to clear obstacles. Time your second jump during the brief glowing pulse to succeed!<br>⬅️➡️ <strong>Impulse Left / Impulse Right</strong> – Make precise adjustments mid-air or on the ground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful — one mistake can send you tumbling back! The path is tough, and every second counts. Your skill, reflexes, and timing will determine how far you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 Don’t worry — the game includes multiple <strong>checkpoints</strong>, so if you fall, you can try again from a safe spot without starting over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗💨 <strong>Check out the GIFs below</strong> to see these mechanics in action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Checkpoint</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class